title: High Ceilings--Loft Style Apt--No Broker Fee--No Amenity Fees
posting_body: ['No brokers fee', 'No amenity fee', 'A Truly HUGE Flex 1 w/ Two Separate Living Areas, Tons of Closets, & LIGHT', 'TONS of Awesome Exposure for more Natural Direct SUNLIGHT – SOUTH FACING !!', 'State of the art kitchen equipped with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances.', 'Our World Class Amenities include 24 Doorman and concierge services as well as a virtual doorman system, an expansive courtyard on the lobby level, a state of the art fitness center, media room, children’s playroom, tenants lounge, bicycle storage, cold storage, package room, parking, outdoor dog run/park complete with dog washing station, a 9th Floor Terrace with Absolutely Stunning Views of the 59th Street Bridge, NYC Skyline, & LIC, in addition to an immense roof-deck complete with cabanas & reserve-able grilles with panoramic views of the NYC, Queens, and Brooklyn Skyline.', 'For more info or a pvt showing', 'Feel free to contact me at anytime']
